    "text": "A comparative transcriptome analysis was performed on wild types, landraces, and improved cultivars of broomcorn millet at seeding and filling stages. The analysis identified genes selected during domestication and improvement. Variations in gene expression patterns between wild types and landraces, and between landraces and improved cultivars, were evaluated to explore molecular mechanisms of domestication and improvement.",
